== 發行 ==
=== 評價 ===
《天降奇兵》獲得多為負面的評價。《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》從五顆星中給了電影兩顆星，主要批評電影的敘事能力和缺乏深度<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/ReviewComplete.asp?FID=9460 | title=''The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen'' | publisher=[[Empire_(film_magazine)|''Empire'' magazine]] | accessdate=2011-05-17 | archive-date=2012-10-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020121947/http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/ReviewComplete.asp?FID=9460 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於177位專業影評人新鮮度僅17％<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/league_of_extraordinary_gentlemen/ | title=''The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen'' | publisher=Flixster | work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate=2011-05-17 | archive-date=2011-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629004316/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/league_of_extraordinary_gentlemen | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根據36條評論分數只有30（滿分100），負評居多<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-league-of-extraordinary-gentlemen | title=''The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen'' | publisher=''[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]'' | accessdate=2011-05-17 | archive-date=2010-11-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101103234542/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-league-of-extraordinary-gentlemen | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
電影首週票房2307萬5892美元排於《[[神鬼奇航：鬼盜船魔咒|神鬼奇航：鬼盜船魔咒]]》之後登亞軍<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=leagueofextraordinarygentlemen.htm | title=''The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen'' | publisher=''[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]'' | accessdate=2011-05-17 | archive-date=2012-11-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102192052/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=leagueofextraordinarygentlemen.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。加拿大和美國的票房約6646萬5204美元，英國為1260萬3037美元、西班牙為1203萬3033美元。全球總計1億7926萬5204美元<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=leagueofextraordinarygentlemen.htm | title=''The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen - Foreign Gross'' | publisher=''[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]'' | accessdate=2011-05-17 | archive-date=2012-10-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023104316/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=leagueofextraordinarygentlemen.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

